<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/insert.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <title>Index</title>
  </head>
  <body>

    {{>navheader}}

    <div class="insertplant-center">   

        <h1>Add Your Own Plant</h1>
        <p>Welcome to our personalized plant collection page! Here, you can create your own collection of plants and learn more about their unique characteristics and care requirements. You can add your own plants to the collection, so you can keep track of your own collection and share your knowledge with others. Whether you're a seasoned plant parent or just starting out, this page is the perfect resource for discovering and caring for all types of plants.</p>
        
        <form action="/auth/insertplant" method="POST" class="insertplantform">
            <label for="plant_type">Plant Type:</label>
            <select name="plant_type">
                <option value="Annual">Annual</option>
                <option value="Climbing Plant">Climbing Plant</option>
                <option value="Fern">Fern</option>
                <option value="Flowering Plant">Flowering Plant</option>
                <option value="Fruit tree">Fruit tree</option>
                <option value="Grass">Grass</option>
                <option value="Ground Cover">Ground Cover</option>
                <option value="Perennial">Perennial</option>
                <option value="Shrub">Shrub</option>
                <option value="Tree">Tree</option>
                <option value="Vegetable">Vegetable</option>
            </select>

            <label for="plant_name">Plant Name:</label>
            <input type="text" name="plant_name">

            <label for="uses">Uses:</label>
            <input type="text" name="uses">

            <label for="plant_family">Plant Family:</label>
            <select name="plant_family">
                <option value="Asteraceae">Asteraceaeual</option>
                <option value="Brassicaceae">Brassicaceae</option>
                <option value="Convolvulaceae">Convolvulaceae</option>
                <option value="Crassulaceae">Crassulaceae</option>
                <option value="Ericaceae">Ericaceae</option>
                <option value="Hydrangeaceae">Hydrangeaceae</option>
                <option value="Lamiaceae">Lamiaceae</option>
                <option value="Liliaceae">Liliaceae</option>
                <option value="Nephrolepidaceae">Nephrolepidaceae</option>
                <option value="Oleaceae">Oleaceae</option>
                <option value="Poaceae">Poaceae</option>
                <option value="Pteridaceae">Pteridaceae</option>
                <option value="Ranunculaceae">Ranunculaceae</option>
                <option value="Sapindaceae">Sapindaceae</option>
                <option value="Solanaceae">Solanaceae</option>
            </select>

            <label for="season">Season:</label>
             <select name="season">
                <option value="Fall">Fall</option>
                <option value="Spring">Spring</option>
                <option value="Spring, Fall">Spring, Fall</option>
                <option value="Spring, Summer">Spring, Summer</option>
                <option value="Summer">Ericaceae</option>
            </select>

            <label for="soil_type">Soil Type:</label>
            <select name="soil_type">
                <option value="Loose, fertile soil">Loose, fertile soil</option>
                <option value="Moist, well-drained soil">Moist, well-drained soil</option>
                <option value="Rich, well-drained soil">Rich, well-drained soil</option>
                <option value="Well-drained soil">Well-drained soil</option>
            </select>

            <label for="min_temperature_requirement">Min Temperature Requirement:</label>
            <input type="number" name="min_temperature_requirement">

            <label for="max_temperature_requirement">Max Temperature Requirement:</label>
            <input type="number" name="max_temperature_requirement">

            <label for="min_humidity_requirement">Min Humidity Requirement:</label>
            <input type="number" name="min_humidity_requirement">

            <label for="max_humidity_requirement">Max Humidity Requirement:</label>
            <input type="number" name="max_humidity_requirement">

            <button class="button-3" type="submit">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </div>   

  </body>

  {{> footer}}
</html>
